items.biography:
Fern Valley Farms is a family-owned organic CBD hemp farm in sunny southern Oregon. All products are grown organically without pesticides, microbials, mycotoxins, heavy metals, etc. and are 3rd party independent lab-tested for these. We offer many high-terpene strains of Indica, Sativa & hybrid CBD flower. All of our tinctures, wax and lotions are made right here in house by our team. The results are some of the finest CBD products available anywhere.

Sign up: https://fernvalleyfarms.com
